(2) The Board shall consist of— (a) one member chosen by the Minister who shall be designated as Chairman; (b) one member representing the growers of Virginia flue-cured tobacco chosen by the Minister; (c) one member representing the growers of Oriental tobacco chosen by the Minister; (d) one member representing the growers of Burley tobacco chosen by the Minister; (e) not more than three members representing the buyers of tobacco chosen by the Minister.
