(5) Whenever representation on the Board of any two or more of the categories of membership thereof provided for by subsection (2) of section four becomes vacant, the Minister may perform all of the functions and duties of the Board until such time as, by appointment, such categories are duly represented, and all such appointments to the Board necessary to complete the representation of such categories shall, in such event, be made by the Minister within three months of the date of the vacancy last occurring before the Minister exercises his powers under this subsection.
