(b) for the purposes of paragraph (a), prescribe the manner in which the Board shall determine the weight of such tobacco which any registered grower of that class or grade of tobacco may offer for sale in the Republic or for export on consignment in the specified period, and the weight so determined shall be the marketing quota of such registered grower for the purposes of this Part.
